">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin: 0px;"><span styl=
e=3D"font-family: tahoma, new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" data-mc=
e-style=3D"font-family: tahoma, new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;"><=
span style=3D"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;" data-mce-style=3D"mso-ansi-languag=
e: EN-US;" lang=3D"EN-US">The ANR funded CoSWoT project [</span><a href=3D"=
https://www.insa-lyon.fr/fr/coswot" target=3D"_blank"><span class=3D"LienIn=
ternet"><span style=3D"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;" data-mce-style=3D"mso-ans=
i-language: EN-US;" lang=3D"EN-US">https://www.insa-lyon.fr/fr/coswot</span=
></span></a><span style=3D"mso-ansi-language: EN-US;" data-mce-style=3D"mso=
-ansi-language: EN-US;" lang=3D"EN-US">] aims at building a distributed sof=
tware architecture on constrained embedded devices with two main characteri=
stics&nbsp;: (1) it will use ontologies to declaratively specify the applic=
ation logic and the semantics of exchanged messages&nbsp;; (2) it will prov=
ide reasoning capabilities to embedded devices to distribute computation. I=
t will highly simplify the development of applications that include Web of =
Things (WoT) devices&nbsp;: the platform will enable the development and ex=
ecution of smart decentralized WoT applications with heterogeneous devices.=
 Application domains are e-agriculture and smart buildings.</span></span></=
p><p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin: 0px;"><span style=3D"font-family:=
 tahoma, new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" data-mce-style=3D"font-f=
amily: tahoma, new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" lang=3D"EN-US">At =
LIRIS, our team works on a scenario with data from sensors deployed in buil=
dings (temperature, humidity, presence, CO2, local weather station, and als=
o electricity power and energy consumption with smart plugs). This scenario=
 includes a platform for sensor management (SoCQ4Home), semantic management=
 of data streams in the CoSWoT platform, and the design of a set of applica=
tions using sensor data (dashboards for users, automatic triggering of aler=
ts or actions).</span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin: 0px;"><sp=
an style=3D"font-family: tahoma, new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" =
data-mce-style=3D"font-family: tahoma, new york, times, serif; font-size: 1=
1pt;" lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margi=
n: 0px;"><span style=3D"font-family: tahoma, new york, times, serif; font-s=
ize: 11pt;" data-mce-style=3D"font-family: tahoma, new york, times, serif; =
font-size: 11pt;" lang=3D"EN-US">In this context, this postdoc (or engineer=
) position will focus on the following steps&nbsp;:</span></p><p class=3D"M=
soNormal" style=3D"margin: 0px;"><span style=3D"font-family: tahoma, new yo=
rk, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" data-mce-style=3D"font-family: tahoma, =
new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p><=
p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin: 0px;"><span style=3D"font-family: ta=
homa, new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" data-mce-style=3D"font-fami=
ly: tahoma, new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" lang=3D"EN-US">a) pro=
pose a semantic modeling for this scenario (buildings, sensors, measures) a=
ccording to the semantic model proposed in the project, in particular a mul=
ti-dimensional modeling of sensor data streams, and potentially propose enh=
ancements of the semantic model&nbsp;;</span></p><p class=3D"MsoNormal" sty=
le=3D"margin: 0px;"><span style=3D"font-family: tahoma, new york, times, se=
rif; font-size: 11pt;" data-mce-style=3D"font-family: tahoma, new york, tim=
es, serif; font-size: 11pt;" lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p><p class=3D"Ms=
oNormal" style=3D"margin: 0px;"><span style=3D"font-family: tahoma, new yor=
k, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" data-mce-style=3D"font-family: tahoma, n=
ew york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" lang=3D"EN-US">b) propose and defi=
ne interesting applications in the context of Smart Building, and their tra=
nslation in the context of the CoSWoT project&nbsp;;</span></p><p class=3D"=
MsoNormal" style=3D"margin: 0px;"><span style=3D"font-family: tahoma, new y=
ork, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" data-mce-style=3D"font-family: tahoma,=
 new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin: 0px;"><span style=3D"font-family: t=
ahoma, new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" data-mce-style=3D"font-fam=
ily: tahoma, new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" lang=3D"EN-US">c) en=
hance the current sensor management platform (SoCQ4Home, with EnOcean senso=
rs) and contribute to the development of the CoSWoT platform, in order to i=
ntegrate sensor data streams from the sensors&nbsp;;</span></p><p class=3D"=
MsoNormal" style=3D"margin: 0px;"><span style=3D"font-family: tahoma, new y=
ork, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" data-mce-style=3D"font-family: tahoma,=
 new york, times, serif; font-size: 11pt;" lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;</span></p>=
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin: 0px;"><span style=3D"font-family: t=
